title: Sean O'Connor
description: SEAN O'CONNOR (Conan, comedy, comedy writer!) lays down an incredible YMIW: funny, thoughtful, DARE I SAY MOVING? Yes I do. And also very, very funny. So glad he could come down. He was great on the live one in Indiana, and really takes it home here. ENJOY YOU WEIRDOS!!
